page.title: 13Living In Keynsham In 1985
page.content: far from the High Street.After school I like going down to Manor Playing Field which has swings,a slide and a see-saw.The field is quite big_it has goal posts so you can play football. Also there is some horses near by so I like going up there and feeding them. { In Keynsham there is plenty of things to do.I like dancing,swimming,and Brownies.The swimming pool is heated and has a great big floating dragon. They have plenty of sports too like tennis,gym,and karate.The dancing class I go to is very good.Mrs Veale teaches us flick kicks,step flicks,and many other steps.At Brownies you go for walks,dance and sing.I also have four pets,a cat called Twinkie and 3 guinea pigs.
